title: StarTalk Live! from SF Sketchfest 2016 (Part 2)
description: This week we’re still on Mars with Andy Weir, author of “The Martian”, and Dr. Jim Green, Director of NASA’s Planetary Science Division. Join Bill Nye, Eugene Mirman and Maeve Higgins for Part 2 of our show recorded live at SF Sketchfest. ADULT LANGUAGE.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
